vote.title: Authorize a professional engineering services contract with HDR Engineering, Inc. to provide three traffic corridor studies at the following locations: Masters Drive from U.S. Highway 175 to Military Parkway, St. Augustine Road from U.S. Highway 175 to Military Parkway, and Camp Wisdom Road from Cockrell Hill Road to Interstate Highway 35 - Not to exceed $853,093.32 - Financing: General Fund
